<i>Captain Darui!</i>

2
00:00:29,188 --> 00:00:33,456
I'll take over the
watch. You should
get some rest, sir.

3
00:00:33,488 --> 00:00:35,190
{\an1}Maybe I will.

4
00:00:40,958 --> 00:00:42,726
Black Panther!

5
00:00:43,293 --> 00:00:46,227
{\an1}[screaming and growling]

6
00:00:48,861 --> 00:00:51,895
{\an1}Captain... Darui?

7
00:00:51,929 --> 00:00:56,431
{\an1}Man... it's enough to
make a guy doubt everyone.

8
00:00:56,465 --> 00:00:59,065
{\an1}When fakes keep popping
up and attacking like this.

9
00:00:59,099 --> 00:01:00,765
Hey!

10
00:01:01,367 --> 00:01:02,766
Uh, my bad.

11
00:01:02,799 --> 00:01:06,067
Anyway, we've pretty
much gotten all the
enemies on the beach.

12
00:01:06,101 --> 00:01:09,202
So, for now, we're
gonna withdraw to
the hills.

13
00:01:09,235 --> 00:01:10,869
{\an1}Uh, right.

14
00:01:15,405 --> 00:01:20,639
{\an5}[sigh] This is duller
than that fight with
my two predecessors
form The Cloud.

15
00:01:34,544 --> 00:01:35,945
This is bad...

16
00:01:35,978 --> 00:01:36,644
Huh?

17
00:01:36,678 --> 00:01:38,480
{\an1}What's the matter,
Shikamaru?

18
00:01:38,512 --> 00:01:39,947
That.

19
00:01:42,948 --> 00:01:47,816
{\an1}<i>White Zetsu's powers have</i>
<i>destabilized the entire</i>
<i>Allied Shinobi Forces.</i>

20
00:01:53,651 --> 00:01:57,686
You mean because of
how everybody completely
distrusts everyone else?

21
00:01:57,719 --> 00:01:59,720
{\an1}Yeah. It's bad.

22
00:01:59,754 --> 00:02:03,654
{\an1}Sometimes mental exhaustion
can take a worse toll than
physical fatigue...

23
00:02:03,688 --> 00:02:05,223
{\an1}So, how do
we fix it?

24
00:02:05,256 --> 00:02:07,990
{\an1}How can we start
making everybody
feel less suspicious?

25
00:02:08,024 --> 00:02:11,125
{\an1}Confirm who people are
using secrets only their
friends would know?

26
00:02:11,158 --> 00:02:12,493
