has a strategy for
identifying the fakes.

30
00:02:20,128 --> 00:02:22,062
{\an1}What!? They already
came up with a plan!?

31
00:02:22,429 --> 00:02:24,863
Oh, good! You really
had me worried, there.

32
00:02:24,896 --> 00:02:29,499
But, the problem is,
it'll take some time
to implement HQ's plan.

33
00:02:30,032 --> 00:02:32,233
So we'll need a
way to hold out
until then.

34
00:02:32,266 --> 00:02:33,433
Huh!?
[distant screaming]

35
00:02:33,732 --> 00:02:35,434
[gasps]

36
00:02:37,435 --> 00:02:39,468
Gentle Fist!

37
00:02:41,302 --> 00:02:43,736
{\an1}Neji! This is...

38
00:02:43,770 --> 00:02:45,537
I know. You're
right.

39
00:02:49,506 --> 00:02:52,240
[chuckle] Seems we
get to play with
you again..!

40
00:02:52,273 --> 00:02:54,640
{\an1}And this time, we
won't hold back!

41
00:02:55,807 --> 00:02:58,442
[flute music]

42
00:03:12,481 --> 00:03:15,748
