while, you gloomy
piece of crap!

43
00:03:15,782 --> 00:03:18,083
{\an1}Enough, Tayuya. Women
should speak properly.

44
00:03:18,116 --> 00:03:19,483
Oh, shut up, fatso!

45
00:03:24,618 --> 00:03:26,253
{\an1}It's them, all right...

46
00:03:34,356 --> 00:03:38,589
{\an1}I've decided it's time for
you to carry out your first
mission as a Chunin, Shikamaru.

47
00:03:40,525 --> 00:03:45,793
{\an5}<i>(Shikamaru)</i>
<i>With a hastily-assembled </i>
<i>squad, we pursued the group</i>
<i>that had abducted Sasuke</i>

48
00:03:45,826 --> 00:03:50,061
{\an1}<i>We were prepared to</i>
<i>lose a man for every</i>
<i>enemy we killed...</i>

49
00:03:50,094 --> 00:03:52,295
<i>...Kidomaru of</i>
<i>the East Gate...</i>

50
00:03:52,328 --> 00:03:53,996
<i>...Sakon of the</i>
<i>West Gate...</i>

51
00:03:54,029 --> 00:03:56,029
<i>...Jirobo of the</i>
<i>South Gate...</i>

52
00:03:56,063 --> 00:03:57,830
<i>...Tayuya of the</i>
<i>North Gate...</i>

53
00:03:58,830 --> 00:04:00,597
{\an1}The Sound Ninja Four.

