trouble's come back to
haunt us.

55
00:04:04,866 --> 00:04:06,233
Choji, are you
coming?

56
00:04:06,267 --> 00:04:06,966
{\an1}Yeah.

57
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,535
Hey, wait!

58
00:04:08,567 --> 00:04:10,402
All of us should
go fight together!

59
00:04:10,436 --> 00:04:11,469
