<i>No!</i>
[gasp]

60
00:04:12,803 --> 00:04:15,770
{\an1}If the fakes somehow
infiltrate us during
the chaos of battle,

61
00:04:15,804 --> 00:04:18,405
{\an1}then the confusion
could break up the
entire unit!

62
00:04:18,439 --> 00:04:22,039
