and I will stop
those four alone!

63
00:04:22,073 --> 00:04:25,107
We know those guys
better than anyone, and
how we can stop them.

64
00:04:25,140 --> 00:04:26,308
Yeah.

65
00:04:26,341 --> 00:04:28,341
But let me make
this clear...!

66
00:04:28,375 --> 00:04:32,709
{\an1}Even if it looks like
us, if it moves, it's
an enemy!

67
00:04:32,743 --> 00:04:34,610
{\an1}Attack without mercy!

68
00:04:34,644 --> 00:04:35,511
Yeah, but...

69
00:04:35,545 --> 00:04:38,112
{\an1}Isn't that right,
Captain Darui!?

70
00:04:38,145 --> 00:04:40,913
Just as I would expect
of Shikaku's son.

71
00:04:40,946 --> 00:04:43,580
{\an1}I think you're making the
right call on this one.

72
00:04:43,613 --> 00:04:48,416
<i>Sorry to keep</i>
<i>relying on you...</i>

73
