85
00:06:36,355 --> 00:06:37,922
{\an1}They're so tough!

86
00:06:42,023 --> 00:06:43,492
[shouting]

87
00:06:46,392 --> 00:06:48,159
Thank you
so much!

88
00:06:48,192 --> 00:06:49,460
Get to safety!

89
00:06:49,494 --> 00:06:50,527
{\an1}[affirming grunt]

90
00:06:54,129 --> 00:06:55,828
Indiscriminate
killing....

91
00:06:55,862 --> 00:06:58,096
{\an1}This method of
attack, it's...

92
00:06:58,130 --> 00:07:03,031
{\an5}Yes. It's a special
thread created by
mixing chakra with a
unique bodily secretion.

93
00:07:03,065 --> 00:07:07,534
In fact, only the
Gentle Fist can
cut this thread.

94
00:07:07,567 --> 00:07:10,502
Hinata, gather some
Gentle Fist users.

95
00:07:10,535 --> 00:07:12,602
Take them to find
and rescue our men!

96
00:07:12,901 --> 00:07:15,369
{\an1}I understand. But,
what about you?

97
00:07:15,402 --> 00:07:18,904
