103
00:07:35,177 --> 00:07:38,411
{\an1}What took you
so long...?

104
00:07:38,445 --> 00:07:41,112
Yeah, right. You're
one to talk...

105
00:07:41,146 --> 00:07:43,946
How many years do
you think it's been
since then?

106
00:07:43,980 --> 00:07:47,014
{\an5}Not that I've been
waiting around for
you to come back
or anything!

107
00:07:47,881 --> 00:07:51,916
{\an1}[frightened cries]

108
00:07:52,716 --> 00:07:54,384
[grunting]

109
00:07:54,417 --> 00:07:56,985
