116
00:08:14,458 --> 00:08:19,160
{\an4}In every team of
five, there's always
one who's in the mix
but just dead weight.

117
00:08:19,193 --> 00:08:22,027
{\an1}The guy who's the
butt of everyone's
jokes...

118
00:08:22,060 --> 00:08:27,029
{\an4}When thick comes to
thin, he's cast aside
like the worthless
pawn he is...

119
00:08:27,062 --> 00:08:29,163
And that's who
you are..!

120
00:08:31,297 --> 00:08:32,565
{\an1}Grr...

121
00:08:34,398 --> 00:08:37,266
[choking]

122
00:08:37,566 --> 00:08:41,468
It's over, you
pathetic fat outcast!

123
00:08:47,103 --> 00:08:51,771
{\an8}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>If I hadn't taken the</i>
<i>secret food pill back</i>
<i>then, I'd've been dead.</i>

124
00:08:51,804 --> 00:08:54,005
Did you go
on a diet?

125
00:08:54,206 --> 00:08:56,072
This is so
unlike you...

126
00:09:01,208 --> 00:09:02,208
{\an1}Huh?

127
00:09:02,241 --> 00:09:03,708
[fighting cry]

128
00:09:05,310 --> 00:09:06,876
{\an1}[shouting]

129
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:19,248
