130
00:09:21,415 --> 00:09:31,519
{\an1}[panting breaths]

131
00:09:40,556 --> 00:09:43,658
{\an1}[struggling grunts]

132
00:09:44,658 --> 00:09:47,358
[gasp]

133
00:09:52,027 --> 00:09:53,860
[heavy breath]

134
00:09:56,061 --> 00:09:59,629
