<i>He makes no pointless attacks...</i>
<i>He's been culling information</i>
<i>with every move...!</i>

135
00:09:59,663 --> 00:10:03,264
{\an7}<i>And he's discovered</i>
<i>the weakness behind</i>
<i>my eyes....</i>

136
00:10:03,298 --> 00:10:05,599
[soughs blood]

137
00:10:06,499 --> 00:10:08,466
{\an8}<i>Impressive...</i>

138
00:10:09,366 --> 00:10:12,934
{\an7}<i>He's the strongest</i>
<i>opponent I've ever</i>
<i>fought.</i>

139
00:10:15,368 --> 00:10:17,303
You're mine!

140
00:10:17,636 --> 00:10:19,304
Fang Over Fang!

141
00:10:20,237 --> 00:10:21,804
{\an1}Multi-Leg Hurricane!

142
00:10:27,073 --> 00:10:29,874
{\an8}[chuckle]

143
00:10:29,907 --> 00:10:32,141
{\an8}I'm getting used
to this dead body.

144
00:10:32,174 --> 00:10:34,042
{\an7}You're taking
too long, just
kill them!

145
00:10:34,075 --> 00:10:36,943
{\an8}Even though you're
dead you haven't
changed a bit!

146
00:10:36,976 --> 00:10:39,743
{\an1}[growling]

147
00:10:49,248 --> 00:10:51,782
[chuckle]

148
00:10:52,549 --> 00:10:53,382
[growls]

149
00:10:54,182 --> 00:10:55,350
[gasp]

150
00:10:55,650 --> 00:10:57,218
[grunt]

151
00:10:58,084 --> 00:11:01,385
{\an1}[growling and barking]

152
00:11:01,751 --> 00:11:07,820
{\an8}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>Heh. I must be a lousy</i>
<i>master for you to bite</i>
<i>me like that.</i>

153
00:11:08,222 --> 00:11:12,755
[growling]

154
00:11:12,789 --> 00:11:14,823
{\an7}This fool! He's
not even worried!

155
00:11:14,856 --> 00:11:18,625
Don't underestimate
us just because
your dog grew up.

156
00:11:22,793 --> 00:11:24,794
{\an1}Akamaru, Wolf Fang
