Flute! Chains of
Fantasia!

167
00:12:23,349 --> 00:12:25,049
{\an1}[♪ Flute Music ]

168
00:12:25,083 --> 00:12:27,016
{\an8}<i>This is bad...</i>

169
00:12:27,684 --> 00:12:30,385
{\an8}<i>This is... a...</i>
<i>Genjutsu..?!</i>

170
00:12:31,018 --> 00:12:37,053
{\an1}[♪ Flute Music ]

171
00:12:37,621 --> 00:12:42,122
{\an8}<i>My body... I</i>
<i>can't... move...</i>

172
00:12:45,123 --> 00:12:48,924
{\an1}[♪ Flute Music ]

173
00:12:48,957 --> 00:12:53,593
{\an4}<i>(Shikamaru Thinking)</i>
<i>Tayuya pulls her victims</i>
<i>into her genjutsu with</i>
<i>her melody...</i>

174
00:12:53,627 --> 00:12:58,662
{\an4}<i>...We have jonin capable</i>
<i>of countering genjutsu,</i>
<i>but with direct contact</i>
<i>between one another</i>

175
00:12:58,695 --> 00:13:02,029
{\an1}<i>forbidden right now, I</i>
<i>can't rescue those </i>
<i>under it's control...</i>

176
00:13:03,230 --> 00:13:04,497
[gasp]

177
00:13:06,298 --> 00:13:07,265
{\an1}[♪ Flute Music ]

178
00:13:07,298 --> 00:13:08,299
[groans]

179
00:13:16,034 --> 00:13:20,069
This is bad. Any
closer and she'll
get me too...

180
00:13:20,103 --> 00:13:23,537
{\an7}<i>You're in no position</i>
<i>to be worrying about</i>
<i>others, you little rat!</i>

181
00:13:23,571 --> 00:13:29,072
It appears that she now
has a greater range than
she used to have...

182
00:13:29,106 --> 00:13:31,806
{\an3}[gasp]

183
00:13:42,910 --> 00:13:46,012
<i>[evil chuckle]</i>

184
00:13:46,580 --> 00:13:48,613
{\an1}Well, well! You've
gotten nimble there,
fatso!

185
00:13:53,081 --> 00:13:54,515
[gulp]

186
00:13:55,882 --> 00:13:58,083
