204
00:15:30,785 --> 00:15:32,017
Damn it!

205
00:15:32,051 --> 00:15:33,084
Huh?

206
00:15:33,117 --> 00:15:34,885
{\an1}[grunt]

207
00:15:35,452 --> 00:15:37,119
You say something?

208
00:15:37,153 --> 00:15:38,320
What!?

209
00:15:38,353 --> 00:15:40,721
That flute of yours is
seriously annoying...

210
00:15:40,754 --> 00:15:43,789
...but if I can't
hear it, it doesn't
matter.

211
00:15:43,821 --> 00:15:45,656
{\an1}A cheap trick!

212
00:15:45,989 --> 00:15:47,023
{\an3}Huh?

213
00:15:47,057 --> 00:15:50,924
{\an1}Anyway, I can pretty much
guess what you'll say.

214
00:15:50,957 --> 00:15:56,360
{\an4}You want to tell me that you
and your friends are stronger
because of a Curse Mark or
something like that, right?

215
00:15:56,393 --> 00:15:58,461
However...

216
00:16:02,529 --> 00:16:07,431
{\an4}I was able to defeat
this guy using the
secret food pill, but
just barely..

217
00:16:07,464 --> 00:16:12,399
Heh. One thing hasn't
changed: You don't
know when to give up!

218
00:16:16,767 --> 00:16:18,268
[shocked]

219
00:16:18,702 --> 00:16:22,302
{\an1}I haven't changed?
No, you couldn't be
more wrong!

220
00:16:30,372 --> 00:16:31,972
{\an1}What...

221
00:16:37,542 --> 00:16:38,408
{\an1}Huh!?

222
00:16:39,042 --> 00:16:41,242
